   <text:p text:style-name="P33"><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span>Iar mura-ntr-adins o fcu pe pmnt <text:line-break/>Slbatica Zn-a pdurii, <text:line-break/>Cci ochii ei negri asemenea sunt <text:line-break/>Cu negrele boabe-ale murii. <text:line-break/>Iar unde e mura, sdit de ea, <text:line-break/>Pot merge neveste i fete, <text:line-break/>Flcilor ns vederea le-o ia <text:line-break/>i junghiuri prin cap le trimete! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">i zmeura-anume-o fcu pe pmnt <text:line-break/>Slbatica Zn-a pdurii  <text:line-break/>Obrajii ei rumeni ca zmeura sunt, <text:line-break/>Obrajii i rumenul gurii. <text:line-break/>Iar pe-unde sdete ea zmeur-n vi <text:line-break/>Pot merge femeile-n pace, <text:line-break/>Dar floarea din fa le-o ia la flci <text:line-break/>i galbeni ca faguru-i face. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Iar muchiu sub brazi ntr-adins l-a lsat <text:line-break/>Slbatica Zn-a pdurii, <text:line-break/>Ca muchiul de moale e caldul ei pat, <text:line-break/>Acolo sub umbra rsurii, <text:line-break/>Iar pe-unde e muchi, e pe-acolo i ea: <text:line-break/>Pot merge s eaz copile, <text:line-break/>Flcilor ns odihna le-o ia <text:line-break/>De pier i se-ngroap cu zile!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T14"> </text:span>Ei, parc pe Zn eu nu tiu s-o-nel! <text:line-break/>Neveste i mur s fie! <text:line-break/>Eu stau pe potec i-ain frumuel <text:line-break/>Crarea la fete-n cmpie, <text:line-break/>Iar cnd o s vd eu c Zna mi-e rea <text:line-break/>i-mi fur tria fpturii, <text:line-break/>O prind prin pduri i-o srut i pe ea <text:line-break/>Pe hoaa de Zn-a pdurii!</text:p>
