   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Hora</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">[lipsete]</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n zori</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Supt un mal legata plut,<text:line-break/>Se mai mic-abia. Duios<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Geme apa-n veci zbtut<text:line-break/>Ca prin vis, sub iaz la moar.<text:line-break/>Luna tot mai jos scoboar<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Tot mai jos, mai jos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A, apus! i dintr-o dat<text:line-break/>Nu mai vezi nici deal, nici drum,<text:line-break/>Totu-n zarea-ntunecat<text:line-break/>i-a pierdut i loc i nume,<text:line-break/>Nu cred c-a mai fost pe lume<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Noapte ca acum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Parc-i mort de veacuri satul<text:line-break/>i trudit de-atta clint<text:line-break/>Doarme-adnc ntunecatul<text:line-break/>Codru-n vi, iar la rstoace<text:line-break/>Plopii-au nceput s-i joace<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Frunzele de-argint.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar din aripi bat cocoii,<text:line-break/>Rscolind vzduhul mut.<text:line-break/>Albe-nti i tot mai roii<text:line-break/>Zorile i-ntind lucoarea <text:line-break/>Din zvoi, privighetoarea<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Iari a-nceput!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n miezul verii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O fie nesfrit<text:line-break/>Dintr-o pnz pare calea,<text:line-break/>Printre holde rtcit.<text:line-break/>Toat culmea-i adormit,<text:line-break/>Toat valea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Linitea-i deplin stpn<text:line-break/>Peste cmpii ari de soare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Lunca-i goal: la fntn<text:line-break/>E pustiu; i nu se-ngn<text:line-break/>Nici o boare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Numai zumzetul de-albine,<text:line-break/>Fr-ncepere i-adaos,<text:line-break/>Curge-ntruna, parc vine<text:line-break/>Din adncul firii pline<text:line-break/>De repaos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ct vezi n deprtare<text:line-break/>Viu nimic nu se ivete...<text:line-break/>Iat ns, colo-n zare,<text:line-break/>Mictor un punct rsare<text:line-break/>i tot crete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Poate-i vrun btut de soart<text:line-break/>Care-alearg pe cmpie<text:line-break/>ntr-atta lume moart!<text:line-break/>Dor l mn, griji l poart,<text:line-break/>Domnul tie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Poi acum s-l vezi mai bine:<text:line-break/>E femeie, o srman,<text:line-break/>Strns la piept n scutec ine<text:line-break/>Un copil; i-n srg ea vine,<text:line-break/>Vine-n goan.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De clduri dogoritoare,<text:line-break/>Foc aprins i arde chipul;<text:line-break/>Un cuptor e roul soare,<text:line-break/>i crbune sub picioare<text:line-break/>E nisipul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd ajunge la fntn,<text:line-break/>Jos pe-o pajite srac<text:line-break/>Pune-odorul ei. Din mn<text:line-break/>Salt cumpna btrn<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i se pleac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Scrind, din nou ea crete.<text:line-break/>Mama toarn cu tot zorul<text:line-break/>Ap-n pumni, i se grbete<text:line-break/>La copil i-i rcorete<text:line-break/>Obrjorul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bea apoi i ea pe fug.<text:line-break/>Merge iari dup asta<text:line-break/>La copil i-i d s sug;<text:line-break/>Frnt-apoi, pe-o buturug<text:line-break/>St nevasta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i e linite pe dealuri<text:line-break/>Ca-ntr-o mnstire ars;<text:line-break/>Dorm i-arinii de pe maluri<text:line-break/>i cldura valuri-valuri<text:line-break/>Se revars.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nici un nor vzduhul n-are<text:line-break/>Foc sub el s mai ascunz;<text:line-break/>Nici o pasre prin zare,<text:line-break/>Nu se mic-n lumea mare<text:line-break/>Nici o frunz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Singur vntul, colo, iat.<text:line-break/>Adormise la rcoare<text:line-break/>Sub o salcie plecat<text:line-break/>Somnuros n sus el cat<text:line-break/>Ctre soare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mai e mult! i ca s-i fie<text:line-break/>Scurt vremea, pn pleac,<text:line-break/>El se uit pe cmpie,<text:line-break/>Fluier i nu mai tie<text:line-break/>Ce s fac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Dar deodat se oprete:<text:line-break/>Peste ochi i pune-o mn<text:line-break/>i zmbind copilrete<text:line-break/>Curios i lung privete<text:line-break/>Spre fntn!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Povestea cntrii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ai poate prin lume vro int <text:line-break/>De-alergi, cltorule vnt?<text:line-break/>Prin largile lumi ale zrii, <text:line-break/>Prin taina cea sfnt-a cntrii <text:line-break/>i, singur, pe vremea-nnoptrii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">M-opresc pe-o colin i cnt. <text:line-break/>i-n urm-mi pdurile cnt <text:line-break/>Cu freamt de doin, cu oapte, <text:line-break/>Iar uneori pn-n pmnt <text:line-break/>Cu uier de criv -prin noapte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar care i-e venica int <text:line-break/>De-alergi, cltorule nor?<text:line-break/>Ascult i eu vntul prin vale <text:line-break/>Cum uier doine de jale, <text:line-break/>Iar dac-mi ntmpin n cale <text:line-break/>Tovari, ncepem n cor <text:line-break/>Cntarea ce vntul ne-o cnt: <text:line-break/>Cu murmur prin noaptea cu lun, <text:line-break/>Cu vuiet de aripi n zbor <text:line-break/>i trsnete-n zi de furtun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ai poate pe dealuri vro int <text:line-break/>De-alergi tu, drumee pru?<text:line-break/>in ochii la norul din zare <text:line-break/>S-nv aiurata-i cntare; <text:line-break/>De-i panic, pe-ascunsa-mi crare <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Eu cnt printre lanuri de gru: <text:line-break/>Cnd noru-n vzduh se frmnt <text:line-break/>mi urlu de-a lungul cmpiei <text:line-break/>n goana mea fr de fru <text:line-break/>Slbatecul cnt al mniei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu singur eti fr de int, <text:line-break/>Poete, i-n gnduri mereu? <text:line-break/>Ascult cum i freamt cntul <text:line-break/>Pdurea, prul i vntul; <text:line-break/>E cerul al meu i pmntul, <text:line-break/>i cnt, ca i ele, i eu. <text:line-break/>n urm-mi popoarele cnt <text:line-break/>Cntri de la mine-nvate: <text:line-break/>i tot ce e-n sufletul meu <text:line-break/>E-n sufletul lumii mirate.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe Tmpa </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un nor ivit de ctr-apus <text:line-break/>Se urc-n sus <text:line-break/>Plutind ncet spre miaznoapte <text:line-break/>Iar umbra lui prin vi cznd <text:line-break/>Acum ntunec pe rnd <text:line-break/>Livezi i vii i grne coapte. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vd drumuri albe-n zri senine, <text:line-break/>La margini muni, mai jos coline <text:line-break/>i, ca pe-o pnz zugrvit, <text:line-break/>Orau-n vale-adnc sub mine. <text:line-break/>E pace-n cer i pe pmnt; <text:line-break/>Abia nestttorul vnt <text:line-break/>Venit de peste muni, de-aiurea, <text:line-break/>Tot spune ce din veci a spus <text:line-break/>i pn-n vi, de-aici de sus, <text:line-break/>Se zbate-ncet doinind pdurea.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Pastel</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Publicat n <text:span text:style-name="T5">Pagini literare</text:span>, 1899, nr. 10 (19 dec.)<text:line-break/>Prin viini vntul n grdin<text:line-break/>Ctnd culcu mai bate-abia<text:line-break/>Din aripi, i-n curnd s-alin,<text:line-break/>Iar roul mac nchide floarea,<text:line-break/>Din ochi clipete-ncet cicoarea<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>i-adoarme-apoi i ea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu cred c-a obosit pdurea,<text:line-break/>Cci ziua-ntreag-a tot cntat<text:line-break/>i tace-acum gndind aiurea.<text:line-break/>Sub dealuri amurgete zarea,<text:line-break/>Se-ntunec prin vi crarea<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>i-i umbr peste sat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Peste culmi ncet amurgul moare<text:line-break/>i-ntors cu faa ctr-apus<text:line-break/>D semne nopii din ponoare.<text:line-break/>Ea-mbrac haine-ntunecate<text:line-break/>i linitit din aripi bate<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Plutind tcut-n sus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tciunii-n vatr dau lumin;<text:line-break/>Pe drumul de drumei srac<text:line-break/>Mai vezi fugind cte-o vecin<text:line-break/>S cear cu-mprumut jaratec;<text:line-break/>Grbit, d roate, singuratec,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Tcutul liliac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i tot mai noapte-apoi se face,<text:line-break/>Pduri i ape-adorm acum;<text:line-break/>Din cer scoboar-adnca pace.<text:line-break/>Ici-colo vrun zvor mai sun -<text:line-break/>ncepe-a se zri de lun<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>i-i linite pe drum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Copiii dorm, visndu-i jocul.<text:line-break/>Mai toarce mama. n curnd,<text:line-break/>Pe vatr ea-nvlete focul,<text:line-break/>ncuie uile la tind,<text:line-break/>Se culc-apoi. Iar cariu-n grind<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>S-aude-acum roznd.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Blestemul trdrii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu sfrmate catapulturi<text:line-break/>Turnul muced st-nclinat,<text:line-break/>Iar n poart surii vulturi<text:line-break/>Frnt-i au de mult aripa,<text:line-break/>Stnd s cad-n toat clipa<text:line-break/>Peste pragul fulgerat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ns-n veci vor sta la poart,<text:line-break/>C-i din cer blestem de veci.<text:line-break/>Noaptea-nvie-o oaste moart,<text:line-break/>i-i de coifuri valea plin<text:line-break/>F o cruce i te-nchin.<text:line-break/>Cltorule, cnd treci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Noaptea din ruini rsare<text:line-break/>Tot castelul, precum fu.<text:line-break/>an i ziduri de-aprare,<text:line-break/>Turnuri albe cresc deodat,<text:line-break/>O cetate-nfricoat<text:line-break/>Unde-Agripa cuib avu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar din vi un prin se suie<text:line-break/>Alb de arme, spre castel;<text:line-break/>E tcere-n cetuie,<text:line-break/>Dar stafiile pe coaste<text:line-break/>Repezi vin, o-ntreag oaste,<text:line-break/>Toi ai prinului cu el.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Lupi ce casc largul gurii<text:line-break/>Au pe coif, i parc-au strns<text:line-break/>Toate fiarele pdurii.<text:line-break/>Sunt de-acei ce-au stat n cale,<text:line-break/>Varro tu, otirii tale<text:line-break/>i-au fcut pe-August de-a plns.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd ajunge la cetate<text:line-break/>Albul prin al celor mori<text:line-break/>De trei ori cu pumnul bate<text:line-break/>Repede-n arama porii<text:line-break/>Scri aduc n grab morii,<text:line-break/>Cu berbecii bat n pori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-auzind cum vin barbarii,<text:line-break/>Ua tainiii-o deschid<text:line-break/>i tresar legionarii;<text:line-break/>Ei din brbi, din pr, cu mna<text:line-break/>Iui i scutur rna,<text:line-break/>Ies, alearg, sar pe zid.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sub un ru de creste roii<text:line-break/>Albe coifuri strlucesc,<text:line-break/>i-n amestec furioii<text:line-break/>Respingnd pe cei de-afar<text:line-break/>Cad i mor, se nal iar,<text:line-break/>Rane fac i le primesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Zngt ns n-are-arama<text:line-break/>Cnd se bate scut de scut,<text:line-break/>Tuba nu-i cunoate gama:<text:line-break/>Fr zuzt lancea zboar,<text:line-break/>Iar al spzii-oel doboar<text:line-break/>Cald i strlucind, dar mut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">Pe deasupra lor cu spaim<text:line-break/>Luna se ascunde-n nor,<text:line-break/>Glas de bufnie se-ngaim<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i, cu aripi speriete,<text:line-break/>Lilieci zburnd n cete<text:line-break/>Se izbesc de coiful lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">De-ai avea voi pace-odat,<text:line-break/>Voi ce v luptai mereu!<text:line-break/>Pacea ns nu vi-i dat,<text:line-break/>Ca s tii n venicie<text:line-break/>Dreapta Domnului mnie<text:line-break/>i c-i unul Dumnezeu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cei trdai, ei dorm n pace!<text:line-break/>Vou-al morii dttor<text:line-break/>Partea asta nu vi-o face!<text:line-break/>Voi cnd ai vzut pe-o seam<text:line-break/>C pe Crist cel mort l cheam<text:line-break/>Martor al jurrii lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n nedreapta voastr ur<text:line-break/>Vrnd s-i pierdei, ai fcut<text:line-break/>Cu barbarii-o legtur.<text:line-break/>i-au venit pe-ascuns barbarii<text:line-break/>i-au pierit legionarii<text:line-break/>Ci pe Crist l-au cunoscut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Noapte-a a fost. Pe zid cretinii<text:line-break/>Se luptau pentru-mprat:<text:line-break/>Voi ns-ai deschis, hainii,<text:line-break/>Toate porile cetii<text:line-break/>Dreapta cumpn-a Dreptii<text:line-break/>Iat-acum s-a rzbunat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cei trdai, ei n morminte<text:line-break/>Dorm n pace. ns voi<text:line-break/>V luptai i-acu-nainte<text:line-break/>Cu otirile chemate<text:line-break/>i de-a pururi v vei bate<text:line-break/>Pn-n ziua cea de-apoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Astfel parc-ntruna plnge<text:line-break/>Turnul obosit i el<text:line-break/>De-a vedea tot mori i snge.<text:line-break/>Cci de veacuri vede-ntruna<text:line-break/>Noaptea cum aduc furtuna<text:line-break/>Morii-acetia din castel.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar cnd ziua se revars,<text:line-break/>Pier i ziduri i cohori,<text:line-break/>Ruinat-n deal i ars<text:line-break/>St cetatea trist-n soare<text:line-break/>Dar n noaptea urmtoare<text:line-break/>Vin din nou aceiai mori.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe munte </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fugii cu turma repede spre vi!<text:line-break/>Pe culme-alearg duhul rzbunrii<text:line-break/>Grozavul vnt se zbate-n largul zrii<text:line-break/>i norii-mbrac hain de vpi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sosete-acum! cu ochiul ct cuprinzi<text:line-break/>Furtuna-n srg scoboar-n jos pe coaste,<text:line-break/>i-n urma ei se-ntinde neagra oaste<text:line-break/>i url-n cor: Tu fulgere, s-aprinzi,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu nor, s-ntuneci; vnte, tu s-mprtii!<text:line-break/>Un brad se face ndri, cel mai nalt:<text:line-break/>i prins de vrf, au smuls pe cellalt<text:line-break/>Purtndu-l roat-n largul chip al prtii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe sus se-ntinde-amestecul nespus,<text:line-break/>i Duh n Duh prin aer se frmnt,<text:line-break/>Iar grindina-n vzduh cumplit i cnt<text:line-break/>Cntarea ei de-oel, cznd de sus,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Pe codrul larg ce-n urlete se-ndoaie,<text:line-break/>i sare iar la loc apoi mugind.<text:line-break/>Deodat st. i iat-l, rpind<text:line-break/>Potop din cer turnatul ru de ploaie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se rupe cerul, cade-acum! S-a rupt.<text:line-break/>Sporite neguri hran dau pieririi,<text:line-break/>De-a valma geme-ntreg cuprinsul firii,<text:line-break/>i nu mai tii ce-i sus i dedesubt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acum nici Dumnezeu nimic nu poate.<text:line-break/>Degeaba-ntind ei minile i cer<text:line-break/>n negrul iad, i unul pn-n cer,<text:line-break/>Vrteju-i domn, el singur domn a toate.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Apoi vezi... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Cte fete mndre-n sat<text:line-break/>Toate in cu tine <text:line-break/>Zic i eu! i nu-i pcat,<text:line-break/>Ele tiu mai bine.<text:line-break/>Cnd ncep i eu s joc<text:line-break/>Intr junghiu-n fete<text:line-break/>i s-opresc drumeii-n loc:<text:line-break/> sta-i joc, biete!<text:line-break/>Voi srii ca un ileu,<text:line-break/>Ici e es, ici groap <text:line-break/>Apoi vezi! Frumoasa, eu,<text:line-break/>Voi, pe cte-o schioap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar la plug de-oi vrea, apoi,<text:line-break/>S m las pe coarne,<text:line-break/>Brazda mea nici patru boi<text:line-break/>Nu pot s-o rstoarne.<text:line-break/>Eu din umeri scot un car<text:line-break/>Pn-n dealul mare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mut o piatr de hotar...<text:line-break/>Ce vi-e de mirare?<text:line-break/>Vou i-un butuc vi-e greu,<text:line-break/>Eu ridic o brn <text:line-break/>Apoi vezi! Pe mndra eu,<text:line-break/>Voi, pe cte-o crn!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Beau i eu, i joc, i-art<text:line-break/>C mi-e lumea drag,<text:line-break/>Dar ca voi eu nu m-mbt<text:line-break/>Sptmna-ntreag.<text:line-break/>Ce-mi tot cni de boi i bani?<text:line-break/>I-am gsit eu gata?<text:line-break/>N-aveam cas-acu cinci ani,<text:line-break/>i-a fcut-o tata?<text:line-break/>Palmele, c-mi ard mereu,<text:line-break/>Capul, c mi-e moar <text:line-break/>Apoi vezi! Pe mndra eu <text:line-break/>Voi, pe cte-o chioar!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Andromahe</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iat-i chiotind n cnturi, <text:line-break/>Cupe-ncununnd cu vin; <text:line-break/>Flota cu sprijin de vnturi <text:line-break/>Vjie sub cer senin  <text:line-break/>O, nu fierbi, adnc al mrii, <text:line-break/>i furtuni tu nu strneti <text:line-break/>Ca s-azvrli ndeprtrii <text:line-break/>Rmiele greceti; <text:line-break/>Zeus, nu zgudui tu rotundul <text:line-break/>Cerului cu foc etern, <text:line-break/>Ca s-i vnturi n afundul <text:line-break/>Nopii venice-n Infern!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-am putut scpa de sbii,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Flcri ne-au ncins pe loc;<text:line-break/>Robi ajuns-am pe corbii, <text:line-break/>De-am putut scpa de foc! <text:line-break/>Vai, i de-au scpat o seam <text:line-break/>De robie, unde sunt?<text:line-break/>Chinul sta cum se cheam,<text:line-break/>Cnd de viu eti n mormnt <text:line-break/>Rtcind printre ruine,<text:line-break/>Troia moart-o vor vedea,<text:line-break/>i le-ar fi cu mult mai bine<text:line-break/>Dac-ar fi pierit sub ea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar i-att e mngiere,<text:line-break/>Cu iubiii ti s fii<text:line-break/>La un loc i-ntr-o durere;<text:line-break/>i e dulce gnd s tii <text:line-break/>C cenua ta udat<text:line-break/>De vrun binefctor <text:line-break/>Va zcea amestecat <text:line-break/>Vecinic cu cenua lor! <text:line-break/>ns noi, pe mri, robite <text:line-break/>Urgisiilor ahei, <text:line-break/>Noi ne ducem risipite <text:line-break/>Prin pmnturi fr zei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu mi-ai prevzut mormntul, <text:line-break/>Tu Casandra,i-ai tcut?<text:line-break/>Nimeni nu-i credea cuvntul, <text:line-break/>ns eu l-a fi crezut! <text:line-break/>Astzi n-a pluti spre Ftia , <text:line-break/>ndurnd potop de-ocri; <text:line-break/>Noi n-am suferi robia <text:line-break/>Celei mai miele ri! <text:line-break/>Eu prin Skyros, tu-n Micene <text:line-break/>Roab-a regelui s gemi  <text:line-break/>ara unde cresc Helene <text:line-break/>i se nasc Neoptolemi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Plnge tnguita gloat, <text:line-break/>Plng i eu privind la ea: <text:line-break/>Ah, din lumea asta toat <text:line-break/>Eu am partea cea mai rea! <text:line-break/>l ursc, i el, turbatul,<text:line-break/>Nemilos cu mine nu-i; <text:line-break/>Cel ce mi-a ucis brbatul <text:line-break/>Azi m are-n voia lui! <text:line-break/>ntunerec m-mpresoar, <text:line-break/>Minile pe cnd mi frng, <text:line-break/>i vedenii-n jur mi zboar <text:line-break/>i-mprejuru-mi toate plng </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Plng lopeile, i plnge <text:line-break/>Marea cu murmur amar <text:line-break/>Iat-l, gol i plin de snge, <text:line-break/>Hector, i-i trt de car. <text:line-break/>Risipit-n vnt viaa <text:line-break/>Strop de strop din el s-a stors, <text:line-break/>i, murind, strivit, cu faa <text:line-break/>Bietul e spre Troia-ntors. <text:line-break/>De fiori ncremenete <text:line-break/>Largul apelor adnci, <text:line-break/>i de vaiet lung vuiete <text:line-break/>Golul mucedelor stnci!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i m-ntorc... i mi s-arat <text:line-break/>Sngele-mprocat pe zid, <text:line-break/>i, gemnd cutremurat, <text:line-break/>Lumea ochilor mi-o-nchid. <text:line-break/>Nici o mil n-au mieii! <text:line-break/>De-un copil nepriceput <text:line-break/>Tremurau pierdui aheii <text:line-break/>i-Agamemnon s-a temut. <text:line-break/>O, i sunt viteji! i tat <text:line-break/>Au pe Phoebus! Cum te mint<text:line-break/>i tu nu-i strpeti odat, <text:line-break/>Mndre zeu cu arc de-argint!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Iar prin noapte, cnd, pe puntea<text:line-break/>Tigrului, eu de dureri<text:line-break/>mi ngrop n palme fruntea,<text:line-break/>Vine-ncet printre strjeri<text:line-break/>Hector aducnd de mn<text:line-break/>Pe copil, frumos i blnd;<text:line-break/>Glasul apelor se-ngn,<text:line-break/>Pnzele vuiesc gemnd:<text:line-break/>i pe cnd la piept ne strngem,<text:line-break/>Plnge tat i copil,<text:line-break/>i tustrei prin noapte plngem -<text:line-break/>Evoe,-n Infern, Ahil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, dolopi, i v-amgete <text:line-break/>Gndul c, rznd de sori, <text:line-break/>Azi prin mine se-njosete <text:line-break/>Cel mai vrednic dintre mori! <text:line-break/>C din cercul nemuririi <text:line-break/>Smuls iei-va, voi pgni, <text:line-break/>Cel ce v-azvrli pieririi <text:line-break/>Pe la Xantus, ca pe cni? <text:line-break/>Iar tu crezi c-i trectoare <text:line-break/>Jalea mea pe care-o gem? <text:line-break/>C m vei clca-n picioare, <text:line-break/>Barbare Neoptolem?<text:line-break/> <text:line-break/>Blestemat fie ara <text:line-break/>Care v-a nscut pe toi! <text:line-break/>Ura lumilor i-ocara <text:line-break/>Motenii-o la nepoi! <text:line-break/>Iar pe tine-n rnd cu orbii <text:line-break/>Foamea poart-te prin ui, <text:line-break/>De pe cmpi adune-i corbii <text:line-break/>Oasele-n scrbos culcu; <text:line-break/>i murind, de-i vrea cu mna <text:line-break/>S-i aduni pe-obraz nisip, <text:line-break/>Sa se zvrcole rna <text:line-break/>ngrozit de-al tu chip!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i-n tesalicele maluri <text:line-break/>Ruri milostive sunt <text:line-break/>Ca-n rostogolite valuri <text:line-break/>S dea omului mormnt! <text:line-break/>i greceasca spad scurm <text:line-break/>Pieptul, ca i orice fier, <text:line-break/>Curge de pe-a dnsei urm <text:line-break/>Sngele din cei ce pier. <text:line-break/>i-ori i-n care ri silit <text:line-break/>S triesc, se va afla <text:line-break/>Vrun pmnt care s-nghit, <text:line-break/>Hectore, pe-aleasa ta!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Murind</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe cretet de dealuri e soare,<text:line-break/>Dar umbre-ale nopii prin vi,<text:line-break/>i-n umeda nopii rcoare<text:line-break/>Soldatul, departe de-ai si,<text:line-break/>Se zbate, i geme, i moare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i snger pieptul de-arsur.<text:line-break/>Iar apa se zbucium rar<text:line-break/>Devale, i-alene murmur <text:line-break/>Ah, umed un deget mcar<text:line-break/>S-l puie pe vnta gur !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar trupu-i e frnt de prin cruce.<text:line-break/>Voind s se nale puin,<text:line-break/>De-asear se-ncearc s-apuce<text:line-break/>Cu mnile-o creang de spin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El vede prul ! Msoar<text:line-break/>Cu ochii, trei palme de drum.<text:line-break/>Aa de cnete s moar !<text:line-break/>Se-ntunec vile-acum,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Iar noaptea grbit scoboar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El parc st-n noapte la pnd,<text:line-break/>Puin rdicat pn-n bru;<text:line-break/>i-i galben de-atta osnd,<text:line-break/>Cu ochii intii spre pru,<text:line-break/>Scrnind ca o fiar flmnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-astmpr-n urm i ine<text:line-break/>Pe inim pumnu-ncletat.<text:line-break/>Apoi cu rsufluri puine,<text:line-break/>Simindu-i tot trupu-ngheat,<text:line-break/>i trage mantaua pe sine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O-ntinde cu dinii i geme,<text:line-break/>Iar gura-i optete duios.<text:line-break/>Eu nu tiu, sunt rugi ori blesteme,<text:line-break/>Dar tiu c-a pierit fr vreme<text:line-break/>Flcul voinic i frumos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">C iat-l scldat n sudoare,<text:line-break/>i-acum e tcere prin vi.<text:line-break/>El nici nu mai simte ce-l doare<text:line-break/>i nici nu mai strig pe-ai si,<text:line-break/>Nu plnge, nu geme. El moare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se-ncinge cu aur cununa<text:line-break/>Pdurii de brad de pe culmi,<text:line-break/>Doinete i vntul ntr-una<text:line-break/>Cntnd somnoroilor ulmi,<text:line-break/>Strbate prin vale-acu luna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea vede pe mortul din vale<text:line-break/>i trece tcut, pe sus.<text:line-break/>Ce roie-a fost, i pe cale<text:line-break/>Ce alb se face spre-apus.<text:line-break/>De jale pesemne, de jale !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>(1899)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Strigoiul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acum tu poi s-o-ntrebi, c n-ar rspunde.<text:line-break/>Punndu-i pe genunchi uitatul fus,<text:line-break/>Pe-un scaun vechi, n faa vetrei scunde<text:line-break/>Privete-n foc, i Domnul tie pe-unde<text:line-break/>E gndul mamei dus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">E singur pe lume, i pierdut.<text:line-break/>Brbatul ei, sunt ani de cnd a dat<text:line-break/>Pe Bistria-n Vrtej, mnnd o plut.<text:line-break/>Rmase-aa de Dumnezeu btut<text:line-break/>S toarc biata-n sat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-acum de-abia s-a-nchis mormntul bine<text:line-break/>Pe singuru-i copil ajuns flcu,<text:line-break/>i-au i-nceput cu oapte-ntre vecine <text:line-break/>N-au pe-altu-n sat ? Dar cine tie, cine ?<text:line-break/>De ce-ar vorbi de ru ?!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea-i vede-n col mormntul sur, iar irul<text:line-break/>De plopi nali se zbucium cntnd,<text:line-break/>i-i plin de-un vuiet jalnic cimitirul <text:line-break/>Tresare-acum. Ea d s-i toarc firul,<text:line-break/>i-l uit n curnd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Deodat-ntoarce capul fulgerat<text:line-break/>Spre prag. Dar nu-i nimic. I s-a prut<text:line-break/>C sun clana ca din mni purtat.<text:line-break/>Se-ntoarce spre fereastr-apoi, deodat,<text:line-break/>Dar geamul e tcut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se uit lung la geam. E noapte-afar<text:line-break/>i lun-n cer ca ziua. i-i trziu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Se uit-n jur prin coluri, spre cmar...<text:line-break/>i-apoi se-ntoarce-ncet spre u iar <text:line-break/>Tcere i pustiu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se scutur, cu frig, pe scaun mama<text:line-break/>i-nchide ochii strns, i st pe loc.<text:line-break/>A fost icoana-n col, pocnise rama.<text:line-break/>Ea-i terge ochii umezi cu nframa<text:line-break/>i iar privete-n foc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar iat pe mormnt lumini s-arat.<text:line-break/>Cum stau intii spre om, de prin strmtori<text:line-break/>Doi ochi de lupi prin noapte-ntunecat,<text:line-break/>Aa doi ochi de foc spre cruce cat<text:line-break/>i stau nemictori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Motan zbrlit cu spete-ngrbovite<text:line-break/>St-n culme de mormnt, venit din iad :<text:line-break/>Dar crucea nu-l nfrunt ! i topite<text:line-break/>Se sting ncet luminile-ndrcite<text:line-break/>i-n hul nopii cad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe scaun a-ngheat acum btrna,<text:line-break/>Cci tot mai mult se zbate pe mormnt<text:line-break/>i salt zbuciumat-n sus rna,<text:line-break/>Prea c din adnc o zvrl cu mna <text:line-break/>Fereasc Unul sfnt!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-aud horcituri de om ce moare<text:line-break/>Strpuns de cel ce-i sta-n genunchi pe piept,<text:line-break/>Rsare-un cap cu plete zburtoare,<text:line-break/>Un piept, i-un&apos;om, i iat-l n picioare<text:line-break/>St-n zarea lunei drept.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cum glgie la vaduri apa-n grle,<text:line-break/>Gngave vorbe rari din gura-i ies,<text:line-break/>i joac erpi n sn, n pr oprle,<text:line-break/>Iar pieptu-i rsuflnd, bolnav s-azvrle<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mai tare i mai des.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Trndu-i giulgiul alb spre gard se duce.<text:line-break/>Iar roii-i ochi ca dou flcri ard.<text:line-break/>ntinde-un bra Spre par ca s-l apuce,<text:line-break/>Punnd piciorul stng pe-o cruce<text:line-break/>El sare peste gard.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nici paii nu-i sunar pe morminte,<text:line-break/>Nici umbr-n urma lui nu s-a vzut,<text:line-break/>Ca surul nor de fum trecu-nainte <text:line-break/>Sub gard s-aud oftri, s-aud cuvinte<text:line-break/>i plnge-un glas gemut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se zbate-n chin drcesc, el vars par.<text:line-break/>i smulge giulgiul putred de pe trup,<text:line-break/>Se pleac-n patru brnci n chip de fiar,<text:line-break/>S-azvrle peste cap, i-n urm iar,<text:line-break/>Pzii-v c-i lup !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i bate-n flci, s mute i s-omoare,<text:line-break/>Iar spume verzi i picur fierbini<text:line-break/>Din gura cu gingii sngertoare,<text:line-break/>Pmnt mprtie-n urm-i, din picioare,<text:line-break/>i mrie-ntre dini.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu labele pe giulgi, el l sfie,<text:line-break/>i-n gur-l ia i-l scutur prin vnt.<text:line-break/>Turbat el roade-n dini cte-o fie,<text:line-break/>Frmnt-n loc pmntu-n vrmie<text:line-break/>i muc din pmnt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">l vezi ? Pe dup gard n goan vine<text:line-break/>i iese-n drum; spre sat alearg-acum,<text:line-break/>Iar coada ridicat-n sus o ine <text:line-break/>De eti pe drum, d-n lturi, tu cretine,<text:line-break/>S nu te afle-n drum!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Acum e la rscruci i st i scurma<text:line-break/>i-adurmec pmntul ntr-un loc <text:line-break/>Suflarea bietei mame-acum se curm,<text:line-break/>C n-afl-ntoars lupul nici o urm.<text:line-break/>i-alearg val de foc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El intr-n sat, ia drumul peste vale.<text:line-break/>ncep s urle-a moarte cinii-n sat<text:line-break/>i fug spre ui de tinzi, ferind din cale;<text:line-break/>n turn, n clopot limba url-a jale<text:line-break/>Un dang nfiorat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cretinii ci nu dorm cu spaim cheam<text:line-break/>Pe Maica lui Christos i-aprind grbit<text:line-break/>Tmie i-usturoi pe-un vas de-aram.<text:line-break/>Ea singur-n cscioar, biata mam.<text:line-break/>St chip nmrmurit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea-l vede cum despic-n dou satul ;<text:line-break/>E cre la pr i nalt ct un viel,<text:line-break/>nvrte ochi de flacr, turbatul,<text:line-break/>i-i iute-n mers i-i negru ca pcatul<text:line-break/>C-i duhul ru n el.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea nici nu-nchide ochii s nu-l vaz,<text:line-break/>Nu tremur de el, nu-i face cruci.<text:line-break/>Czu icoana-n col. Putea s cad !<text:line-break/>Strigoiul e aici, el e-n ograd,<text:line-break/>Srit peste uluci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acum la ua tinzii, iar zvorul<text:line-break/>S-arunc singur, zgomotnd din loc.<text:line-break/>E-n tind. E n prag. A pus piciorul<text:line-break/>n cas-acum. A-ntrat ucigtorul.<text:line-break/>Dar ea se uit-n foc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu ochii fioroi privete-o clip<text:line-break/>La ea i-nvrtejit s-azvrle-apoi,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu dinii-i prinde-a poalelor arip <text:line-break/>Ea sare-atunci nebun-n&apos;sus i ip:<text:line-break/> Srii c e strigoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Att a fost. Nici alt cuvnt, nici lupt ;<text:line-break/>Cci nimeni din vecini n-o auzi.<text:line-break/>Dar moart o gsir-n zori, i supt,<text:line-break/>i-n jurul ei buci de hain rupta,<text:line-break/>Cretinii-a doua zi.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Crciunul n tabr </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41">(Pe Cmpia Smrdanului, 1877)<text:line-break/>i-acei ce de-a pururi au glume,<text:line-break/>Azi tremur mui i-ngheai<text:line-break/>n jalea cea fr de nume;<text:line-break/>Pustii ei simt, i-aruncai<text:line-break/>Departe la margini de lume.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41">Iar codru-ngropat e-n zpad;<text:line-break/>Nu-i u, nu-i cale, nu-i loc.<text:line-break/>n haine ca-n zi de parad,<text:line-break/>in pnea-ngheat la foc,<text:line-break/>Stnd unul ntr-altul grmad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">E freamt n zare: e tunul,<text:line-break/>Ori cntec de clopot din sat?<text:line-break/>Crciunul e astzi, Crciunul.<text:line-break/>Flcii in capul plecat,<text:line-break/>i plnge-necat cte unul...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ard vesele flcri pe vatr;<text:line-break/>i-ai casei, la mas, gtii.<text:line-break/>Vin oaspei, i canele latr;<text:line-break/>Le ies nainte grbii<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ai casei pe pragul de piatr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar pnea pe mas, vecin,<text:line-break/>Pe neted-ntinsul tergar,<text:line-break/>Cu vinul din oala cea plin;<text:line-break/>i nsui bunicul, cel rar<text:line-break/>La vorbe, azi rde i-nchin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">Cu crpa la spate legat<text:line-break/>Nevasta se-nvrte, avnd<text:line-break/>Spre toi cte-o vorb-mbunat<text:line-break/>i, locuri pe lavii fcnd,<text:line-break/>E suflet i inima toat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">Din leagn i blbie-odorul,<text:line-break/>Se lupt din mni i e-n zor<text:line-break/>S-i duc la gur piciorul,<text:line-break/>Afar e soare sub nor,<text:line-break/>Dar hain de aur e norul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-i hohot de rset n strad,<text:line-break/>i nsui bunicul acum<text:line-break/>Se-ndoaie spre geamuri s vad<text:line-break/>Amestecul vesel din drum<text:line-break/>i lupta cu plumbi de zpad:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O ceat mai mare de fete<text:line-break/>Au prins de flci, mai puini.<text:line-break/>i-aprins e lupta-ntre cete,<text:line-break/>i toi de zpad sunt plini<text:line-break/>i-n gura i-n snuri i-n plete...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-aici, n pierduta cmpie,<text:line-break/>Sunt ninse crrile-acum,<text:line-break/>Se zbucium vntu-n mnie,<text:line-break/>Iar corbii-n pribeagul lor drum<text:line-break/>Dau roate prin zarea pustie...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>(1900)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">trengarii de pe Cynthus</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P32">Departe-n zarea culmii<text:line-break/>Pe Cynthus, pe sub ulmii<text:line-break/>Ce dorm pe la cascade,<text:line-break/>Din umed fapt de zori<text:line-break/>ntins-au lan de hori<text:line-break/>O gloat de-oreade<text:note text:id="ftn2" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>3</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="Footnote"><text:span text:style-name="T7">n mitologia greac, nimfe ale grotelor i munilor.</text:span></text:p></text:note-body></text:note>.<text:line-break/>i rd n joc i cnt<text:line-break/>i-n tropote frmnt<text:line-break/>Pmntul ud de rou,<text:line-break/>i tot mai mult s-aprind <text:line-break/>Iar ulmii stau privind<text:line-break/>Minunea asta nou.<text:line-break/>Ici una cu vestmntul<text:line-break/>Sltat pe pulpi; iar vntul<text:line-break/>Dezleag colo znii<text:line-break/>Frumosul bru cu flori,<text:line-break/>Dincoace-omortori<text:line-break/>Rsar din umbr snii.<text:line-break/>Ce zimbete irete,<text:line-break/>i ochi aprini, i plete<text:line-break/>Lsate-n vnt plutirii!<text:line-break/>Pe umerii lor goi<text:line-break/>Cum plou roii foi<text:line-break/>Din plete trandafirii!<text:line-break/>Iar ele rd mai tare;<text:line-break/>i tot mai cu mirare<text:line-break/>Pletoii ulmi s-apleac<text:line-break/>Cu ochi aprini i mari:<text:line-break/>Rsufletele rari<text:line-break/>n piept acum le seac.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i-un ulm, prndu-i poate<text:line-break/>De rs acestea toate,<text:line-break/>Da hohote, nebunul.<text:line-break/>i toi c-un gind la fel<text:line-break/>Rd ulmii dup el;<text:line-break/>Treizeci de ulmi ca unul.<text:line-break/>De spaim zpcite,<text:line-break/>Se-ntorc dezlnuite<text:line-break/>i caut prin zare<text:line-break/>Copilele-adpost.<text:line-break/>Dar asta ce-a mai fost?<text:line-break/>Iar ulmii rd mai tare.<text:line-break/>Din rpi acum gramad<text:line-break/>Ies satirii s vad<text:line-break/>Ce hohote rsun<text:line-break/>Pe culme, i curind<text:line-break/>Vin roiuri ntrebnd,<text:line-break/>i tot mai muli s-adun.<text:line-break/>Alt hohot se pornete,<text:line-break/>Rd ulmii nebunete<text:line-break/>Nevrnd nici s-i aud.<text:line-break/>Vuiesc din mii de guri<text:line-break/>Vaznd ce strmbturi<text:line-break/>Fac satirii de ciud.<text:line-break/>n loc ca s-i mpace<text:line-break/>Pe satiri, rsu-i face<text:line-break/>Mai ri, se smulg de barb<text:line-break/>i sar cu pas de ap,<text:line-break/>Cu pumnii-i dau n cap<text:line-break/>Trintinud-se prin iarb.<text:line-break/>La urm, ns, iat<text:line-break/>Rd satirii deodat:<text:line-break/>Rd ulmii c gsir<text:line-break/>Pe satiri caraghioi,<text:line-break/>Rd satirii voioi<text:line-break/>De ulmi c-nnebunira.<text:line-break/>i-acolo-n zarea culmii<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i satirii i ulmii<text:line-break/>Cu rsul lor urmar<text:line-break/>Mai tiu eu cit i cum <text:line-break/>Dar cred c rid i-acum<text:line-break/>i-or rde i la var.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lumnrica</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Rd cu toii! Singur mortul<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Tace-aa pe loc.<text:line-break/>Vine-o fat, pune ortul<text:line-break/>Mortului pe piept, sub cruce,<text:line-break/>O srut i se duce<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>S se-nire-n joc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Patruzeci de mni ateapt<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Focul cltor:<text:line-break/>Ce primete mna dreapt<text:line-break/>Cealalt mn-alung -<text:line-break/>Vezi abia o roie dung<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Dintr-un punct n zbor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar zburnd, slbete focul<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Aripile-i scad,<text:line-break/>Se-nguntete-ntruna locul<text:line-break/>Pn n-o s mai rmn:<text:line-break/>Cui i se va stinge-n mn<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>andra de bord?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar ea zboar, zboar-n pace.<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Grabnic ntr-un glas<text:line-break/>Colo-n col:  Ei, na-i-o, drace!<text:line-break/>i-ntr-aceeai clip unul<text:line-break/>Mai din dos:  Ei, vezi nebunul,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Mi-o zvrlit-o-n nas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/> Petre, tu? Hai, scoate banul<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Sun-l s-l vedem.<text:line-break/>Ce-ai tu, Petre, cu trmul?<text:line-break/> O s-mi fie na, cumetre.<text:line-break/> Las&apos; c tim! Eti vrednic, Petre,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Vrednic s te bem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sun banul pe comoar <text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>i din nou la gard<text:line-break/>Zboar, tot mai mic, zboar<text:line-break/>Ca un fulg lumnrica,<text:line-break/>Multe, multe mni, de frica<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Stingerii, se ard.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">Sfriesc fclii aprinse<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Lng mort acum.<text:line-break/>Numai gturi vezi ntinse,<text:line-break/>Numai ochi pierdui cu firea,<text:line-break/>Stnd ini n urmrirea<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Flcrii de drum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33">Iat-o, nu-i! aa-i de slab:<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Dar deodat ce-i?<text:line-break/>Nu tiu care drac de bab,<text:line-break/>Stnd pe vatr sus, ca apul<text:line-break/>Ca s vad peste capul<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Altora femei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-a plecat prea mult, s vad<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>i, deodat, hu!<text:line-break/>i nu singur s cad,<text:line-break/>A mai tras cu ea vro dou -<text:line-break/>Ce s v mai spun eu vou<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Hohotul ce fu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Haid&apos;! S-a stins lumnrica.<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Zarv-ntre femei:<text:line-break/> Aoleu, e la Florica!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Nu-i la ea; e la Ileana.<text:line-break/>Iar flcii trag cu geana,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Rd apoi i ei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Rd cei moi cu albe plete,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Iar Ileana-i foc.<text:line-break/>Hohotete-un stol de fete,<text:line-break/>Iar nevestele s-adun;<text:line-break/> Vino, f, nu fi nebun,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Vezi c-i numai joc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cum st proptit n coate,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Unul din btrni,-<text:line-break/>Cel mai mare domn pe toate,<text:line-break/>Pn i pe-un fir de sare,<text:line-break/>Dac d cel sfnt i-l are,-<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Ia nuiaua-n mni:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> Haid&apos;, i de i-or pune fato,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Braul dup gt,<text:line-break/>O s-i rspopesc, c iat-o!<text:line-break/>Am porunci de la vldic:<text:line-break/>Cine nu mi-o ti de fric<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Nu mi-o ti, i-att!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-a putea eu spune fostul<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Cum a fost ntreg,<text:line-break/>Meter, neic, mi-ar fi rostul!<text:line-break/>Poate-a isprvi pe gheme<text:line-break/>Pn mni cam pe-ast vreme,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Ei, dar nu m leg!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dintr-o vorb hohot iese,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Hohot dintr-un semn,<text:line-break/>Stau urcai acum pe mese,<text:line-break/>Pe cuptor, pe unde-apuc<text:line-break/>i nevrnd gsesc s-aduc<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Rsului ndemn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Singur mortu-n sfnta-i pace<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Doarme somnul lui -<text:line-break/>S te miri de el c tace!<text:line-break/>Iar lumnrica zboar,<text:line-break/>Rde-n drumul ei uoar,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Iat-o iar c nu-i.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Las&apos; s doarm-n pace mortul,<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>Om fr noroc!<text:line-break/>Vine-o fat, pune ortul<text:line-break/>Mortului pe piept, sub cruce:<text:line-break/>O srut i se duce<text:line-break/> <text:s text:c="7"/>S se-nire-n joc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">(1902)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Regele Pontului </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aproape de strmbele maluri<text:line-break/>Corabia-n fug trecea,<text:line-break/>Cntau despicatele valuri,<text:line-break/>Cntau i matrozii pe ea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar noaptea i marea-mpreun<text:line-break/>Fceau armonie deplin <text:line-break/>Pe ape lucire de lun<text:line-break/>i pace-n vzduhul senin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Trezit de puterea cntrii,<text:line-break/>Aude, tresare prin somn<text:line-break/>Din groap-i, pe marginea mrii,<text:line-break/>Puternicul Schiiei domn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ncet se ridic-ntr-o mn,<text:line-break/>Se uit pe mare mirat;<text:line-break/>Crunta lui barb btrn<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i umple tot pieptul cel lat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Furtunile mrii grozave<text:line-break/>Urlat-au, cu trsnet trecnd,<text:line-break/>i valuri, i brne de nave<text:line-break/>Trosnit-au pe groap-i cznd,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i neamuri strine trecur<text:line-break/>Pe-acolo, cu vuiete mari:<text:line-break/>Pe groapa lui corturi fcur<text:line-break/>i-altare drumeii barbari.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El ns-ntre dune pierdute<text:line-break/>Somn fr curmare i greu<text:line-break/>Dormit-a ! de treizeci de sute<text:line-break/>De ani el dormit-a mereu !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-acum l deteapt-o cntare,<text:line-break/>Un plnset de glasuri ce pier.<text:line-break/>Se uit de-a lungul pe mare<text:line-break/>LA nav, la maluri, la cer,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La lun cum alb strluce,<text:line-break/>i-i pare c n-o mai vzu,<text:line-break/>i-i pare c-aminte-i aduce<text:line-break/>De-o lume uitat, ce fu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O raz din vremile-apuse<text:line-break/>E cntecul celor ce trec:<text:line-break/>Odat i dnsu-l tiuse,<text:line-break/>Copil al pmntului grec.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i vesel, ca valul i vntul,<text:line-break/>Cntndu-l, pe mare-a trecut,<text:line-break/>Uitatu-l-a ns-n pmntul<text:line-break/>Acelor ce domn l-au fcut !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ce i-a pierdut el viaa<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu taberi pe esuri, cu oti?<text:line-break/>Eu, mare,-i cunosc ie faa,<text:line-break/>Tu, mare, tu nu m cunoti !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ce-a alergat el prin lume<text:line-break/>Ctnd i mrire i-averi?<text:line-break/>Lsat-a prin veacuri vrun nume?<text:line-break/>i parc-au fost toate ca ieri !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Copil el s fie-acum iari<text:line-break/>Pe ionice maluri, srac,<text:line-break/>S-alerge cu dragii tovari,<text:line-break/>S vnture lumea pe plac !</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar nava se duce, se duce<text:line-break/>Dincolo de-albastru-orizont,<text:line-break/>Tot Pontul de lun strluce<text:line-break/>i-un rege se plnge pe Pont.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">(1902)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1">Cntece de vitejie </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(1904)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-ai mnat prin veacuri turmele pe plai, <text:line-break/>Din stejarul Romei tu mldi rupt, <text:line-break/>i-i cntai amarul din caval i nai. <text:line-break/>Dar cumplit tu fost-ai cnd te-au dus n lupt <text:line-break/>tefan i Mihai. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd i-or pune piedici dumanii s cazi <text:line-break/>Spada ta s fie i de-acum, romne, <text:line-break/>Fulger care-aprinde, vnt ce rupe brazi, <text:line-break/>i te-ncrede-a pururi c vei fi i mine <text:line-break/>Tare cum eti azi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sus ridic fruntea, vrednice popor! <text:line-break/>Ci vorbim o limb i purtm un nume, <text:line-break/>Toi s-avem o int i un singur dor <text:line-break/>Mndru s se nale peste toate-n lume <text:line-break/>Steagul tricolor!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Imnul studenilor </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cntm libertatea i numele sfnt <text:line-break/>Al rii strvechi i-al acestui pmnt! <text:line-break/>Iubirii de neam, ce de-a pururi ne-a fost <text:line-break/>O pavz-n lupte i-n pace-adpost <text:line-break/>Cntmu-i supremul ei cntec. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu vesele glasuri de tinere firi, <text:line-break/>Cuprini de-amintirea strbunei mriri, <text:line-break/>Spre soare ni-e gndul i mergem spre el, <text:line-break/>Lumina ni-e int i binele el <text:line-break/>Triasc-ne ara i neamul! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu dreapta-nlat spre Tatl de sus <text:line-break/>Jurat-am tot ce strmoii ne-au spus: <text:line-break/>Unire-ntre frai, i pe Domn s-l iubim <text:line-break/>i-altarul de jertf-al naiunii s fim <text:line-break/>i sufletul neamului nostru. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar dac protivnicii numelui tu <text:line-break/>Cu oti ar veni ca s-i fac vrun ru, <text:line-break/>Ridic-te mndr i nu te-ngrija, <text:line-break/>Cci inima noastr e inima ta; <text:line-break/>Tu-ncrede-te-n fiii ti, mam. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">lar dac-ar pieri de pe-ntregul pmnt <text:line-break/>Iubirea de neam i-al credinei avnt: <text:line-break/>Azilul lor vecinic gsindu-l n noi <text:line-break/>Le-am crete, ca iar s le dm napoi <text:line-break/>Mai tari i mai trainice lumii.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec ostesc </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Caii sar i fru-i muc <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Jos prin vi e fum de puc, <text:line-break/>Corbi s-arat croncnind. <text:line-break/>Stau de-atac dumanii gata <text:line-break/>Uite-o-n zbor ntunecata <text:line-break/>Moarte-acum spre noi venind! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">tim cu toii ce ne-ateapt! <text:line-break/>Sus spre Domnul mna dreapt <text:line-break/>Ridicai-o dar, jurnd! <text:line-break/>Pentru sfnta noastr lege, <text:line-break/>Pentru neam i pentru rege <text:line-break/>Toi c-o inim i-un gnd! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu mi te mhni, copile, <text:line-break/>Cine are-n lupt zile <text:line-break/>Nu s-atinge plumb de el. <text:line-break/>Ori aici, ori dealtdat, <text:line-break/>Moartea nou tot ni-e dat <text:line-break/>Fiecruia-ntr-un fel. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Glas de trmbi rsun <text:line-break/>i coloanele s-adun <text:line-break/>Fii cu inim, copii! <text:line-break/>Nu e rece glas de-aram, <text:line-break/>Ci e jalnic plns de mam, <text:line-break/>Plnsul sfintei Romnii! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu ne vezi din cer, Printe, <text:line-break/>Fie-i i de noi aminte <text:line-break/>C suntem i noi ai Ti! <text:line-break/>Fie-i blestemat mormntul <text:line-break/>Cui i calc jurmntul. <text:line-break/>i-am jurat pe cer, flci! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Las tobele s bat! <text:line-break/>Cpitane, du-ne-odat <text:line-break/>Unde-i foc i unde-i fum. <text:line-break/>Steagu-n vnt! Triasc ara! <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vesel sune-acum fanfara, <text:line-break/>Dumnezeu cu noi de-acum!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dorobanul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Albina, 1900, nr. 1 (1 oct.)<text:line-break/>Strecurai prin plumbi i sbii, dorobanii drum deschid. <text:line-break/>Inimoi s-azvrl prin anuri i de-a valma sar pe zid. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i era prin an pierire i vzduhul tremura, <text:line-break/>Iar dincolo, prin redut, moartea cea de veci era. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tropot de picioare multe, fum i abur ca-ntr-un iad, <text:line-break/>Vuiet cum l fac prin balt cei ce-alunec i cad. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar roiau mereu flcii rsrii ca din pmnt, <text:line-break/>Valuri ce-necau reduta, scufundndu-se-n mormnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Unul singur n roirea de viteji, un doroban, <text:line-break/>Zbovea trudit pe-o scar, rsrit i el din an. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cei sosii, cu scri, n juru-i i fceau n grab rost <text:line-break/>i treceau, urmndu-i alii, iar el tot pe unde-a fost. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Apucase strns cu dreapta parapetul, ca-n asalt, <text:line-break/>Dar era prea slab, pesemne, zidul lunecos i nalt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iat-un cpitan, din urm, aducnd n foc pe-ai lui, <text:line-break/>D de el. Cu srg, biete! Ce-ntrzii de nu te sui? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El abia-i ntoarce capul. N-am putere s m urc. <text:line-break/>M trudesc cu stnga numai! Bat-l Dumnezeu de turc! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ii la sn, se vede, dreapta! Pune dreapta! N-o inea. <text:line-break/>Cum n-a pune-o, i-i sub scar! Uite-o, stai s calci pe ea. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Ajutndu-i cpitanul, el se nal-ncet, ncet, <text:line-break/>D un chiot i se nal, rsrind pe parapet. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vede jos ncierarea lupttorilor voinici, <text:line-break/>Un amestec orb ca-n cuibul rscolitelor furnici. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El nal-n vnt chipiul, strig-un nume drag i sfnt <text:line-break/>i-apoi sare de pe ziduri, n redut i-n mormnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea era pmnt al nostru, smuls din sufletul turcesc, <text:line-break/>i voia i el s moar pe pmntul romnesc!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dunrea i Oltul </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dunrea vorbea cu Oltul: <text:line-break/>Tu, copile drag al meu, <text:line-break/>Zbuciumat tu vii la vale <text:line-break/>Tulbure mereu <text:line-break/>Plou mult la voi la munte, <text:line-break/>Sate i cmpii de-neci, <text:line-break/>Ori i-e firea ta de-a rupe <text:line-break/>Maluri pe-unde treci? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Rup i maluri cteodat <text:line-break/>i fac holdele de pier, <text:line-break/>Iar cnd plou mult la munte <text:line-break/>Cap de om eu cer. <text:line-break/>Dar nu-i asta, maic sfnt, <text:line-break/>Nu de asta-s tulburat, <text:line-break/>Ci de cte vd mi-e mil, <text:line-break/>Maic, i-i pcat! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu, pe unde-alergi prin lume, <text:line-break/>Vezi i ri i muni frumoi, <text:line-break/>Neamuri ce-i vorbesc ferice <text:line-break/>Graiul din strmoi. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Toate laud pe Domnul, <text:line-break/>Libere-a tri cum vor, <text:line-break/>Vesele fiind de viaa <text:line-break/>i de soarta lor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vezi i-aici poporul nostru <text:line-break/>Cel din veac adus pe-aici, <text:line-break/>Sprintene i mndre fete <text:line-break/>i flci voinici. <text:line-break/>i i-e drag ara asta <text:line-break/>De romni, cci te iubesc <text:line-break/>Dar tu nu cunoti de-a-ntregul <text:line-break/>Neamul romnesc! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu de unde vin, mhnitul, <text:line-break/>Furios spre es scobor, <text:line-break/>Cci de unde vin, e spaim. <text:line-break/>Groaz i fior. <text:line-break/>Tot romni sunt i pe-acolo, <text:line-break/>Neam din veac pe-aici adus, <text:line-break/>Dar pe gtul lor i astzi <text:line-break/>Jugul este pus. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei n-au voie s-i vorbeasc <text:line-break/>Graiul strmoesc ce-l au, <text:line-break/>Iar n coasta lor de-a pururi <text:line-break/>Suliele stau. <text:line-break/>Sfnta libertate este <text:line-break/>Nume gol pe-al lor pmnt: <text:line-break/>Cei nedrepi sunt cei puternici, <text:line-break/>Singuri au cuvnt! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ah, de mila lor eu, maic, <text:line-break/>Vin aa de tulburat, <text:line-break/>i de ciud pe dumanii <text:line-break/>Cei ce l-au clcat. <text:line-break/>Iar de-nec i mal i oameni, <text:line-break/>Nu mai tiu ce fac nici eu <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>C m simt de-atta jale <text:line-break/>Tulbure mereu!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pentru libertate </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Universul literar, 1903, nr. 19 (12 mai)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plngem, da, c prea ne doare! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu pe noi! Crescui n chin </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ne-amintim de-un timp cu soare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-l cunoatem cel puin! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">PIngem pe copii, srmanii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C-ntr-al temniii mormnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i ncep n noapte anii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Netiind ce-i soare sfnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plngem, da, i strns ne strngem </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lng-olalt, ci suntem, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar s tii c nu ne plngem </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca nebunii cari se tem. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Robi, menii prin jocul sorii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noi ai chinului am fost, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>ns nu, i nu, ai morii! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu ctm noi adpost </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nici n mil, nici n rug; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Asta cear-o de la voi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cel ursit s fie slug </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar n-o cerei de la noi! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vom rbda, privind n faa </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Oriicui, i-a orice chin, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C noi tim c-i mult via </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i n noi, i-n cei ce vin. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Blestemai pieri-vor regii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cari s-abat din drumul drept </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ne-ai adus stricarea legii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i ne stai cu mna-n piept. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">O, i-n loc s-avei ruine, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">V mndrii cu ce-ai adus: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar puterea, tii voi bine, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu vi-a dat-o Cel-de-sus, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nici Eternul Domn! Vi-e dat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>De-un vremelnic din Infern! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Deci vi-e binecuvntat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i la voi va fi-n etern! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lumile-au vzut mirate </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ct de mult iubiri voi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">uierul de bici ce bate </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fr de mil oameni goi! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar i pentru noi rmne </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Timp ah, cine poate ti! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">uierul acesta mine </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnt al lui Tirteu va fi! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar din lanul ce-azi ne strnge </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pot s ias spzi, i pot </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Spzile s vad snge, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu de-al nostru ns tot! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i sfritul tu veni-va </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Azi ori mine,-ori mai apoi! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-o s poi tu sta-mpotriva </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Poate-a celor mai vro doi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar mai tari prin rzbunare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i prin ura lor turbai? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">O s fii destul de tare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot potopul s-l abai? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Eu nu chem aceast vreme, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar tiranul bra al tu </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Face totul ca s-o cheme, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ru ngrmdind pe ru.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntecul cel vechi al Oltului </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vine, tat, Oltul mare; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Malul stng de-abia-l zresc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Las s vie Oltul mare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C, romni de cnd triesc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Oltul tot la piept ne are </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-i al nostru i ne tie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i nu bate cu mnie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Malul cel basarabesc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vine mare, las s vie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>C ni-e sol dumnezeiesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vine, tat, Oltul mare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Brazi trsnii rostogolind. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Las s vie Oltul mare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cci ttarii-ncoace tind, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar li-e Oltul n crare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i n-au inim s-l treac </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i speriei se-ntorc i pleac, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cu noi hor nu se prind. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Las s vie, c-i neac, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Neamul nostru mntuind. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vine, tat, Oltul mare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i cu snge-amestecat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Las s vie Oltul mare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C mulimi de oti ttare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">El pe mal a apucat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lifte poart, lifte duce, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lifte, bat-i sfnta cruce; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Oltul capul le-a mncat! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Las s vie s-i apuce </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>C ni-e scut de Domnul dat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Scut i arm </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Domnul sfnt s ne iubeasc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-al su Duh ocrotitor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plin de pace s pluteasc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste ara Romneasca </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-al romnilor popor! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noi prin vremi ce ne-ncercar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Alt arm n-am avut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Numai dragostea de ar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce strmoii ne-o lsar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i pe Sfntul Domn de scut. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar ne-a fost destul atta! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fruntea sus, voi frai ai mei! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Astfel Cerul hotrt-a </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S se nale amrta </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ar, prin puterea ei! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mai fi, mai fr veste </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ne-ai lovit, dumani de voi! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar ce-a fost, a fost poveste! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dragostea de ar este </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i mai tare-acum n noi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i de cine ne-o fi team? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mult a fost, s v rbdm, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nebgai de voi n seam </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Astzi tii voi cum ne cheam, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dac nu, s v-nvm! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Numai Domnul ne iubeasc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-al su Duh ocrotitor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plin de pace s pluteasc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste ara Romneasc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-al romnilor popor!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Oltenii lui Tudor </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Universul literar, 1903, nr. 27 (7 iulie)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vine-un chiot dinspre munte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vine freamt din pduri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tudor domnul vine-n frunte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cu mulimea de panduri! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar din Jiu, din ap sfnt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iese cntec vitejesc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i cu glas de surle cnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot poporul romnesc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Las s-i sune surle-n ar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S-i adune-olteni destui, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ara s-o vedem noi iar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vesel pe urma lui </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mndra patrie romn </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu sub bra de oameni slabi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ci voinic i stpn </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cum a fost sub Basarabi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Zboar corbi pe sus, biete, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Crduri negre se-nvrtesc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i se zbat de-atta sete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i de foame se izbesc: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">N-au s-atepte-oltenii rug </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S le dea de hran-n vi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Oh, ciocoi, te-ajung n fug </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toi rzbuntorii ti! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cine vrea prta s fie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dreptului pe-acest pmnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dup Tudorin s vie! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C-i trimis de Domnul sfnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S ne scape-acum odat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De ciocoi, cci Dumnezeu </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">nsui s-a pornit s-i bat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cum ne bat i ei mereu. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ridicai, romni, Dreptii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Steag cu sfntul George-acum </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Sfintei Legi i libertii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Facei-i odat drum! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cine nu-i cu voi, s tie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C izbit va fi de voi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De cei stranici n mnie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i din leagn de eroi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Domnul Tudor s triasc! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sus cu toii, pui de lei, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pentru ara Romneasc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pentru drepturile ei! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">A-mbrcat cmaa morii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Domnul Tudor, ca Hristos, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar schimba-va pasul sorii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Va trnti tiranii jos!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Srindar</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar Matei n balt stete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pn-n zori, n stuf ascuns, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Frigul nopii l-a ptruns </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>i prin suflet spaim-i dete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C pierirea l-a ajuns. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dumnezeule-al puterii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vezi-m-n ce stare snt! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">F, s scap de-acest mormnt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Deprtndu-mi ianicerii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i m leg cu jurmnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C scurgnd aceast balt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Chiar pe locul unde zac </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mnstire am s fac, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mndr, vesel i nalt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i cu aur am s-o-mbrac. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Turcii ns-l cutar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-alt zi, i nencetat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar Matei n stuf a stat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-alt noapte, mai amar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mort de foame i-nsetat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dat-ai prin Hristos, Printe, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cele nou fericiri! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Scap-m de prigoniri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-i voi ridica, preasfinte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot pe-attea mnstiri! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ruga nu i-a fost primit </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nici acum, i-a stat Matei </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ocolit de agarei </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">nc-o noapte-aa cumplit, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i plngea, gndind la ei: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vai, Printe-al ndurrii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Deprteaz-acest pahar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i scpnd dintr-un amar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mnstiri voi face rii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cte slujbe-n srindar. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-apoi fu, c tot plecar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Nechemaii venetici. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar Matei a strns voinici </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-a gonit pe turci din ar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-a-ngropat i muli aici. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar pe locul unde-n balt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">El ascuns trei nopi a stat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sfnt loca a ridicat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe colin-acum nalt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dup cum s-a i jurat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-apucat-a s cldeasc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Alte nou, rnd pe rnd, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i i-a dat Dumnezeu gnd </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ntr-o zi s le sfineasc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toate-acelai hram avnd. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar n urm ridicat-a </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Un altar dup altar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Domnului cel sfnt ca dar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Cel din urm dndu-l gata, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">I-a pus nume Srindar.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Zece mai </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">n ziua cea sfnt i mare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">La zece-ale lunii lui mai </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se vede-o ciudat-artare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe-un deal de la Plevna, pe-un plai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd zorile-ncep s s-arete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Acolo-n tcutele vi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Din groap ies moartele cete, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De-a pururi jeliii flci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ei vin de prin locuri pe care </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca vechile rni le cunoti, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe unde-au stat anuri odat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Redute, i taberi, i oti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Strivii i cu minile rupte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>i galbeni ca-n jalnicul loc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">n ziua slbatecei lupte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd bieii pieriser-n foc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fac roat, i-o rug murmur </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar Valter i onu, i toi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mai-marii ce-n frunte czur </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stau jalnici acolo-ntre soi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i stau cum st omul ce-ascult </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i nici o micare nu fac; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ateapt cu grij i spaim </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Un semn de departe i tac. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Deodat ei capul ridic, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dau chiot i-n zare privesc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Spre ara din care ieir, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Spre scumpul pmnt romnesc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ascult, cci tunul azi cnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Departe-n iubitul pmnt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Puternic c-n ziua luptrii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar alt fel de cntec, mai sfnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vi-e team c n-o s mai cnte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C moartea v fuse-nzadar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar ara triete! Iar tunul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce limpede-o spune i rar! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ascult... iar ara-i departe, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sunt dealuri la mijloc i vi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i rul cel mare-i desparte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De mame pe bieii flci. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i moartea cea venic-nchise </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe urm-le tristele-i pori, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dr moartea lor via ne dete: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ferice de-asemenea mori! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar ce-or fi optind ei pe vremea </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Ce-ascult cntarea de tun </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Eu nu tiu, cci nimeni nu poate </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe mori s-i aud ce spun. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar cred c se roag, srmanii: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noi liberi pe voi v-am facut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar Tatl din cer s v aib </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De-a pururi sub sfntul su scut!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe drumul Plevnei </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar pe drumul care duce </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">de la Dunre spre munte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Trec romnii zi i noapte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ctre Plevna, merg i vin. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vesele batalioane </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">cu maiorii lor n frunte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ir de care cu provizii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">schilvii n haine crunte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Scrit i chiu, i tropot </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">pe-acel drum de oameni plin. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ntr-acest pestri amestec, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">scobornd pe dealuri, iat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe-un rzor s-oprise-n cale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">o btrn i gemea, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cu desagii goi pe umeri, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">semn de-o cale-ndelungat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar din vi, urcnd alene </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">se vedea venind o ceat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De drumei din ara noastr </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i s-oprir lng ea. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Bun calea, zise unul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Inima v fie bun, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Oameni buni! Dar unde mergei? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De ne-ajut Dumnezeu, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noi, la Plevna, maic drag. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot la Plevna! Cum ne-adun! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Eu de-acolo viu. Biatul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">mi-e-n rzboi acu de-o lun, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>i m-am dus s-mi vd biatul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">c-i la Plevna i-i al meu. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Repede-mprejur se strnse </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ca prin farmec toat ceata </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca s-ntrebe cum e Plevna? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">cum stau turcii-nchii n ea? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce mai zice Carol-vod, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">cnd o fi rzboiul gata? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-mbtat de potopul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ntrebrilor ea, biata, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i tergea cu palma ochii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i plngnd le tot spunea. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar n urm, ei de grija </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">nopii, ca s nu-i apuce: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S rmi n pace, maic, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">s te vad Domnul sfnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i grbii se ridicar </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">toi de jos, fcndu-i cruce. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Ea, cu ochii plini de plnset, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">privea gloata cum se duce, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-un pustiu simi-mprejuru-i </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ntuneric pe pmnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stete-aa, mereu privindu-i </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i deodat-n fuga mare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ea porni la deal, cu strigt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">s s-opreasc ceata-n loc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd ajunse-abia trgndu-i </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">puintica rsuflare: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dragi cretini, voi unde mergei? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">avei mil i-ndurare, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Eu m-ntorc cu voi acolo </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">la biatul meu, n foc! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar ai fost! La Plevna, maic, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">toate-acum i sunt tiute, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ai vzut i tu biatul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ce mai vrei s vezi acum? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>S te-ntorci, n sat acas; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ia-i toiagul tu i du-te. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noi suntem cu toii tineri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">zor avem i mergem iute, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tu eti slab i puin </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i e mult de mers pe drum. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ea-i ntinse-atunci cu gemet </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">minile, strignd cu jale: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu m batei cu nevrerea, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">c v bate Dumnezeu! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Voi fugi cu voi alturi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i de voi muri pe cale, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot att! M-oi ti aproape </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">de biat! n sat, acas </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">E pustiu, c n-am pe nimeni! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Orice-o fi, m duc i eu!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Mortul de la Putna</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar la Putna-n mnstire, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Noaptea, din tcut mormnt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iese-n plin strlucire </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefan cel viteaz i sfnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lespedea ce-au pus-o popii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste groap,-ncet se d </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ndrt i-n fundul gropii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefan plin de pace st. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar se nal-ncet eroul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Deteptat din lungu-i somn, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Luminat e-ntreg cavoul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i sume viteazul domn. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Albu-i coif strluce-n lun </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar pe zale-i joac zri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De lumini ce se-mpreun </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca-ntr-un basm cu artri. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lunga suli i-o poart </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Rsucind-o-n mndru chip </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Eu credeam c-i umbr moart </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce se mic pe nisip, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Dar e viu! Acum ridic </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ochii si, parc-ar lsa </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste-o oaste inimic </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toat vrjmia sa. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Apoi st plecat i-ascult; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Poate-aude spre Hotin </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vuiet i-alergare mult </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De poloni i turci ce vin, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Poate-aude oti ttare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i nval peste Prut, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ori sosind din deprtare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste munte i-a trecut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Regele Matei! Voi cete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De cazaci i de secui, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dumnezeu acum v dete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Gata iar pe mna lui! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sun zornit de zale, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Strigt mare de rzboi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Ard Moldova noastr-n cale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ci dumani i vechi, i noi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefan tremur-n mnie. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iese din tcutul schit </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Luna-n ceruri, argintie, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cu nori negri s-a-nvelit, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i cumplit din bucium sun </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefan vod; ca un nor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ies oteni i iui s-adun </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Roat lng domnul lor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iat-o, oastea lui voinic, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toi cei buni i tari ai si! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefan spada i-o ridic </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i pornete-n srg spre vi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Luna tot mai mult s-ascunde, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot mai negri nori plutesc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i din vi grozav rspunde </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Buciumul moldovenesc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se tot duce, duce-n noapte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Zgomotul n jos spre Prut, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mai lsnd n urm oapte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Din furtuna ce-a trecut. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">E pustiu la mnstire, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Gol mormntul cel deschis! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toate-au fost o nlucire, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toate repezi ca-ntr-un vis. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu tiu bine-n care parte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefane, te-ai dus cu oti, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tiu c tu te-ai dus departe, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i dumanii i-i cunoti! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Bate-i tefane, printe, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Spulber-i de pe pmnt: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Chiar i mort nva-i minte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cine eti i-ai ti ce sunt.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Stema rii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca un zimbru-ntrtat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd a prins pmntu-n coarne, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Tot ce-n drumul lui a stat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Gata s rstoarne </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca un zimbru-ntrtat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Moldovenii s-au luptat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cu potop de litve. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca un leu sfietor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd cuprins de-arcai se vede, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Prin mulimea de popor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Trsnet se repede </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca un leu sfietor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sar-oltenii-n munii lor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">ntr-un iad de latini. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar muntenii ce-au avut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cuib pe apa Dmboviii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca vulturu-n muni crescut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Aprnd rpiii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pui ai si fcut-au scut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">rii lor i-au abtut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Negrul nor de hoarde. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Zimbru i vultur i leu </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fui cnd mi-a clcat pgnul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Patria i dreptul meu. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i va fi romnul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i de-acum romn mereu, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Zimbru i vultur i leu </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i viteazul lumii.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Fragment epic </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar pe lumea ceealalt scobornd acum flcii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cei czui la Vid pe dealuri i pe esuri la Vidin, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ci sosesc pe rnd n stoluri, adunai n gura vii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stau s-atepte alte gloate cte se vedeau c vin. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Unii terg de iarba ud cte-o sabie-ncruntat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Din pulpana hainei, alii sngele duman l storc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i se laud cu toii i vorbesc cu toii-odat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Precum fac biruitorii din rzboaie cnd se-ntorc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd vzur-aceast gloat, toi acei ce-ndumnir </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe romni de-a lungul vremii, plini de spaim-au tresrit </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Resfirndu-se prin noapte, precum fumul se resfir, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i din margini mai spre margini se topeau necontenit. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cu genunchii plini de tremur i cu gheaa morii-n gur, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mori erau de-a doua oar, ca-ntr-al Orcului noian </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lupttorii din Mikene cnd nglbenii vzur </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Strlucind prin noapte coiful comandantului troian. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar ai notri mori de veacuri, ci pierir prin rzboaie, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Aprnd a lor credin i pmntul romnesc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stau cu ochii int-n noapte i-al lor mijloc l ndoaie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca s-apropie privirea de minunea ce-o zresc: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vd romni, i-aud cuvinte romneti! De-ai lor cu toii! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Umilit venea, iar astzi ce trufa acest popor </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ndrznind dinti o seam, vin sfioi s-i vad soii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot mai muli, cu toii-n urm s-au pornit din noaptea lor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i precum n neastmpr psri grabnice cu zborul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se tot strng de pretutindeni toamna ca s plece stol, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Astfel s-adunau romnii i sporea mereu poporul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Celor mori umplnd de vuiet cmpul meu-nainte gol. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S-a micat acum de-a valma toat lumea-n locuina </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Umbrelor, sunnd ca marea i-ntr-un zbucium nentrerupt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar de-atta nor de duhuri ce-i vdea prin glas fiina </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se prea c-i romneasc toat lumea dedesubt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Strbtnd genuni cu mersul, nesfrit li-e venirea, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ca potopul de puternici i nebiruii ca el </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ci pieir far de urm copleii de nvlirea </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Asiei, i-arcai cu glug din cmpiile lui Gel. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ci au nroit cu snge ruri mari i-ascunse plaiuri. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd prin vile bulgare Ioni-avea loca, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i frumosul grai al nostru printre blbite graiuri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-l pstrau, murind sub steagul ducilor de Fgra. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iat-i, nii vin n frunte cei ce-au crmuit norodul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Principii din muni i banii cu viteze fiare-n scut, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i cu Negru-vod-alturi vine Drago voievodul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Unul fost la Olt de paz, cellalt strjer la Prut. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>i-Alexandru-al crui nume i-astzi codrii-l mai ngn </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tnr i prnd ca Hector cel cu coif fluturtor, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd cu sulia-i grozav, falnic rsucind-o-n mn, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sare-n mndru-i car i umple cmpii Troiei de omor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Trsnet al mniei noastre, Mircea, tu iuete-i paii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ad-i gloatele ce-n clipa bine-potrivitei vremi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Prins-au fulgerul cu palma! Bra, ce pustiind vrjmaii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dunrea ca so de lupt, munii te-ai trudit s-i chemi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce vei fi gndit tu, Mircea, cnd vedeai pornit cum vine </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste muni i peste ape, ca furtuna, Ilderim? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vai, putem noi azi pricepe sufletul ce-a fost n tine, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mai avem simire-n inimi ca-ndeajuns s te slvim? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar dincolo vine-n goan cel ce-n numrate zile </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">A clintit temeiul lumii i-a oprit i vremea-n loc, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cel cu nume sfnt de-Arhanghel cu-al tu nume, Mihaile, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot ca tine de puternic i cu sabie de foc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Munii se retrag din cale-i, iar protivnica sa bard </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Intr-n fier ca-n lemnul putred, pui din oltenescul leu! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Foc de n-ar mai fi, i lege, ca nimic s nu mai ard, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Foc ar nate iar pe lume ochii-acestui Prometeu. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i cu el Frca i Stoica, i-nvrtindu-i buzduganul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Doi Buzeti, ducnd i spaim i-al pieririi-nghe cu ei! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Spuie Neajlovul, Sinane, cte oti pierdu sultanul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i elimberul s spuie cum i-a fost, nebune-Andrei? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Amurat, i-aduci aminte cum sosi grbit odat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i era s-i sparg poarta ca s-i intre-n arigrad? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i ce cale-avea s fac! Dar s-a tnguit vrodat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fulgerul c-i drum departe de la nor pn la brad? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iat-l ns cel din cuibul pus de-otenii teutonici, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">tefan, turnul de-aprare al romnilor, venind </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Suflet mnios i-n toat strlucirea ct-n cronici </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Scris e c-a fost pe vremea cnd el ara strjuind </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">A fcut din oase-un munte i-a-nhat i regi de plete </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i, arnd de ciud cmpul, puse-n jug dumanii lui </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe mnunchiul spzii sale mna lui tot cald stete, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cci el nu tiuse-n via cum s-anin spada-n cui. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">El i-aici e-ntreg n arme i purcede-aprins pe cale, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Parc-a pururi vede-n fa Racova i Podu-Nalt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar de vuietul mulimii i de coifuri i de zale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tremur, rzbit de spaim, tot trmul cellalt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">El i-aici e vntul iernii, i dumanii si sunt pleava! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Urc muni fr de plaiuri, trece Dunri fr pod </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Facei loc! Sosesc ca rul lupttorii din Suceava, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Trec voinicii cei npraznici ai lui tefan voievod! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i Ion Cumplitul vod, jalnic schilvita straj </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">A Moldovei, scut puternic al poporului de rnd, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i nenfricoatul epe, Petru Rare a lui Maj </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vin cu toii de prin noapte, gloate-n urm-le-aducnd. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i hatmani i capi de oaste dai-mi voi acum o sut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De viei, ca s am vreme s-i numesc aici pe toi! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i tu, neam romn, tu astzi stai cu inima pierdut, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fr de zei te crezi pe lume i pustiu tu te socoi. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iat-i gloria de veacuri! Umbre mari din lumea moart, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Ah, c n-am eu glas de tunet ca s pot s le rechem </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ne avem i noi Olimpul, i pe-a veniciei poart </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Am intrat i noi; i-ntr-nsul zei fr de moarte-avem! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce-i aluneci plini de jale ochii umezi pe ruine, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Neam al nostru, ca s judeci drumul schimbtoarei sori? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Soarele din noapte iese, din mormnt puterea vine: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Naterea cea viitoare ne e-n lumea celor mori.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe dealul Plevnei </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">E-n amurg. Pe deal bulgarul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Linitit i mn carul. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Roile nu tiu c plnge </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dealul, pe-unde omul mn; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu tiu boii, c-n rn, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe-unde trec, e numai snge. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noaptea-ncet, ncet scoboar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Lilieci prin aer zboar. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe-unde-a fost cumplire-odat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Doarme-acum ntreaga fire, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Peste-un iad de zvrcolire </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cade-o pace-ntunecat. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Numai luna e pe lanuri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar mai sus, pe sub rdanuri, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Unde-a curs fierbinte plumbul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Duhuri vin din vreme-n vreme, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ct e noaptea-n dealuri geme </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i se zbucium porumbul.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Otirile lui Alah </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noaptea care-ncheie anul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Noaptea sfnt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd cetindu-i El-Coranul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Trist mahomedanii cnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe rpuii prin bti </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noaptea asta tie spune </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>De-o minune </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>La Clugreni prin vi, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cnd e-n jumtate rupt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Noaptea-n cale, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe uitatul cmp de lupt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se pornete-un glas de jale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-apoi multe, i-mprejur </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Din pduri rsar o mie, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Din cmpie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plnge-un nesfrit murmur. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i murmurul crete-ntruna </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>i deodat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Url-n zare ca furtuna, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i prin zarea spintecat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De blesteme i de vnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ies spahii n iruri dese, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Grabnic iese </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Oastea-ntreag din pmnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Cci acum, prin lumea lat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Ies s jure </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Toi cari au pierit vrodat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe cmpiile ghiaure, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ateptnd un semn ceresc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stau gtii, potop s plece </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>i s-nece </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot pmntul cretinesc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ei, cu genele-amorite, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Nal mna, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar din brbile-nclcite </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iui i scutur rna </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i pe cai srind grbii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">nvrtesc dumanii crucii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Sbii lucii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De nval stnd gtii. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Furnicnd din mii de locuri, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Plini de ur; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu blesteme i batjocuri, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Strig toi ca dintr-o gur </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sfntul nume-al lui Isus, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i turbate i-ndrznee </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Mii de fee, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Alergnd, privesc n sus. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar acum, fiind o gloat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Numai una, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Osie-ntr-aceast roat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se ridic Semiluna, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De pe steagul care-n vnt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Geme-o plngere-ntrerupt </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>i se lupt; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iar ce geme e cuvnt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-i a lui Alah cuvntul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Sfnt i mare! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i tcut ca mormntul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-mpietrit-acolo-n zare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Oastea-ntreag st pe loc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Codri, dealuri, ru i lunc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Toate-arunc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ochii-n sus, spre-un semn de foc. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mii de guri atunci n vaier </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>Umplu cerul: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Crucea e, o cruce-n aer! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Turcii toi, zvrlindu-i fierul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Iui se-ntorc ca-ntori de vnt; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Noaptea rde luminat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:s text:c="5"/>i deodat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Intr totul n pmnt.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Graiul neamului </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Poezia a fost pus pe muzica compozitorului T. Cerne.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Fie-a voastr-ntreag ar, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i de cerei, v mai dm, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Numai dai-ne voi graiul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Neamului, i se scular </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>S ne vremuiasc traiul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ci dumani aveam pe lume! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Graiul ni-l cereau anume... </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S-l lsm! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar nestrmutai strmoii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot cu arma-n mini au stat: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Au vzut i muni de oase, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i de snge ruri roii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar din ara lor nu-i scoase </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nici potop i nici furtun. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Graiul lor de voie bun </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu l-au dat! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Astzi stm i noi la pnd, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Graiul vechi s-l aprm; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar pe-ascuns dumanii cat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S ni-l fure, s ni-l vnd. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dac-n vreme tulburat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu ne-am dat noi graiul rii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Azi, n ziua deteptrii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cum s-l dm? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Repezi trec cu vifor anii, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ispitind puterea ta, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Neam romn! Cu ur mare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vor cta mereu dumanii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Graiului romn pierzare; </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar s piar ei cu toii: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu l-am dat, i nici nepoii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Nu-l vor da!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">De profundis </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe sub dealurile Plevnei </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Doarme spaima i fiorul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Soarele-i ascunde faa </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-ngrozit se-ntoarce norul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S se duc-ntr-alte pri. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">O, a fost acolo-n vale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Moarte i pierire-odat, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Iar amara ei cumplire </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Scris vreme-ndelungat </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Povesti-se-va prin cri. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Umbl mai ncet cu plugul, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tu ranule, cu grapa, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Poart-te s dai rna </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mai deoparte-ncet cu sapa </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe colnice cu porumb </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Poate unde scurmi pmntul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tu s vezi c iese snge, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plugul tu s dezveleasc </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vrun voinic ce-n groap plnge </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Zbuciumat de spzi i plumb. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Au venit din muni cu soare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i din vi ntunecate, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Au lsat pustii acas </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stne i cmpii i sate </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-au trecut grozavul ru. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Moarte! Tu aveai cu tine </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Tot alaiul spaimei tale: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Spune tu, putut-ai, moarte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S opreti voinicii-n cale, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S le pui mniei fru? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pe sub dealuri pe la Plevna </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Doarme spaima i fiorul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Plin de grije i-n tcere </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Se strecoar cltorul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Prin pustiul loc de-omor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Eu m tem de-un semn, de-o oapt, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Cci din gropile tcute </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vor iei cei mori cu vuiet, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Sute-n lupt iar cu sute, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Repetnd pierirea lor!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Carol Robert </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Stpnul rii feudale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Rdea de Basarab, pe cale </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Venind cu sutele de-arcai </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Turnai n zale, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce-i pentru-aceti viteji ostai </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">O ar larg de trei pai? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Srmanul vod, cum l cheam, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">O fi-n pmnt acum de team! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce minte-o s-l nv! S-l fac </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S ie seam </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C eu sunt eu, i nu m-mpac </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C-un biet ca el, cioban srac! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Uitat-a c-i nscut s fie </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Pstor de oi i slug mie? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">De barb ns am s-l scot </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Din vizunie. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Ce cini l apr? Socot </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">S-l spnzur eu cu cini cu tot! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Curnd, flci! E plin paharul! </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"><text:soft-page-break/>Auzi ce-mi scrie-acum tlharul </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Dar cine crede el c-ar fi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Maghiarul? </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i regele rznd s-opri </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">i-aceste vorbe le citi: </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Mrite crai! i spui prin carte, </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">C vecinic dinspre-a noastr parte </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">Vrem binele! Suntem cei foti </text:p>
